      <title>印尼预计新工厂的镍价将维持在当前水平附近</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-05/indonesia-sees-nickel-holding-near-current-levels-on-new-plants</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印尼政府预计未来镍价将稳定在当前水平附近，因为该国新建的工厂将抵消不断增长的需求，并保持市场供应充足。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-05/indonesia-sees-nickel-holding-near-current-levels-on-new-plants</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 04:53:23 GMT</pubDate>
